               <p>1213. <persName id="def1-1213-18480515" type="defendantName">
                     <interp inst="def1-1213-18480515" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def1-1213-18480515" type="age" value="21"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def1-1213-18480515" type="surname" value="FRANKS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="def1-1213-18480515" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>
                     <hi rend="largeCaps">GEORGE FRANKS</hi>
                  </persName>
                  <rs id="t18480515-1213-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18480515-1213-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18480515-1213-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="stealingFromMaster"></interp>, stealing a piece of paper with a stamp, de-nothing the payment of 1<hi rend="italic">l</hi>. 15<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.; I sheet of paper, and I book, value 13<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.; the property of <persName id="t18480515-name-259" type="victimName">
                        <interp inst="t18480515-name-259" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18480515-name-259" type="surname" value="HALL"></interp>
