                        <interp inst="t18480515-name-262" type="given" value="EDWARD JAMES"></interp>EDWARD JAMES FOOTMAN.</persName>
                  </hi> On the 13th March I fetched some stamps from the Stamp-office—this stamp has my figures on it—it one that I brought.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
